parameters:
Libra the General Store Owner: Hey, welcome back! It's good
to see you.
Clea: Please take care of the reward.

Libra the General Store Owner: Here's the reward from me...
and the bonus I handed over to the guards.
Clea: Thank you very much, then this is it.
Libra the General Store Owner: Are you sure this is enough?

Libra the General Store Owner: I often get asked about the
reason for my success, and I always tell them it's because I
never miss an opportunity.

Libra the General Store Owner: Anyone can have regrets, but
it takes courage for a merchant to seize the opportunities
right in front of them.
Clea: What is it that you want to say?

Libra the General Store Owner: You, you're the leader of
those people you were with, right?

Libra the General Store Owner: As the leader, don't you have
things you can do for the sake of your comrades?

Libra the General Store Owner: Don't worry, it's not
difficult. Just lend me your body for a little bit, that's
all.

Clea (What I should do... What I can do for everyone...
I...)

General Store Owner Libra: That's fine! You made the right
choice for the sake of your comrades.

General Store Owner Libra: I'll definitely give you a
special reward, so come over here and take off your clothes
for me.

General Store Owner Libra: Hehehe, I won't let you have any
regrets, you know?
Do you want to skip the adult scene?

General Store Owner Libra: Here's your reward, I'll leave it
here. I'll be at the tavern downstairs, so if you feel like
having a second round, call me.
Clea: Ugh, why... why did it have to come to this...
Clea: Why... Ah... Father, Mother... Ugh... I'm sorry...
